      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> For more information on security and using credentials, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Best practices for deploying passwords and other sensitive data to ASP.NET and Azure Websites<ept id=\"p1\">](http://www.asp.net/identity/overview/features-api/best-practices-for-deploying-passwords-and-other-sensitive-data-to-aspnet-and-azure)</ept>."
